_sText: This is my Alpha Release for my currently unnamed map. I am releasing now so that when I leave tommarow (11-21-08) that I can come home to some feedback. Remember this is the ALPHA release, there is still a ton of work to do even before the BETA release. There is a bottom part to the map where I am going to work on next, which was supposed to be the original map, but i decided to go all out. I used a few prefabs in this map: Turnin's Lift NatalyaAF's Toilet (if you dont see this let me know) If I missed anyone please let me know. If you dont see Natalya's toilet in some stalls and only the one valve provides PLEASE let me know, this is my first time using PakRat and I tried to do the best I could =/ Please dont rate before you play, I will know if you did or not
